f11676bfd%5C%22%3EA%20tampon%20for%20cancer%20screening%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETeal's%20test%20screens%20for%20human%20papillomavirus%20(HPV)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20virus%20that%20causes%20more%20than%2099%25%20of%20cervical%20cancer%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20is%20designed%20like%20a%20tampon%2C%20with%20a%20plastic%20applicator%20that%20guides%20a%20squishy%2C%20spongy%20tip%20that%20deploys%20and%20collects%20a%20sample%20from%20inside%20the%20vagina.%20In%20testing%20of%20over%20600%20women%20at%2016%20clinical%20trial%20sites%20nationwide%2C%20Teal%20found%20that%2098%25%20of%20users%20get%20an%20accurate%20test%20result%20on%20their%20first%20try%2C%20and%2094%25%20of%20participants%20preferred%20it%20to%20getting%20their%20test%20in%20a%20doctor's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20results%20are%20mailed%20in%20and%20processed%2C%20Teal%20asks%20patients%20to%20schedule%20a%20follow-up%20telehealth%20visit%20with%20one%20of%20its%20providers%20to%20discuss%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22teal%20health%20wand%20and%20app%20for%20telehealth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e0262a466d2b74ab57e69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeal%20Health%20pairs%20the%20at-home%20test%20with%20a%20virtual%20doctor's%20visit.%3Cp%3ETeal%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20method%20that%20can%20actually%20bring%20screening%20to%20patients%20and%20overcome%20some%20of%20the%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20women%20from%20getting%20appropriate%20screening%20will%20be%20exciting%20and%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Melissa%20Frey%2C%20a%20gynecologic%20oncologist%20who%20directs%20the%20Genetics%20and%20Personalized%20Cancer%20Prevention%20Program%20at%20Weill%20Cornell%20Medicine%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20HPV%20test%20isn't%20the%20only%20component%20of%20a%20Pap%20smear%2C%20Frey%20said%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20important%26quot%3B%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20tests%20still%20can't%20do%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20I'm%20very%20much%20in%20favor%20of%20new%20screening%20modalities%20that%20help%20meet%20patients%20where%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Rachel%20Flink-Bochacki%2C%20an%20academic%20OB-GYN%20in%20New%20York%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BMy%20one%20hesitation%20is%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20other%20things%20that%20happen%20during%20a%20healthcare%20visit%2C%20so%20many%20other%20benefits%2C%20even%20just%20to%20a%20routine%20pap%20smear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20in-office%20pap%20smear%20can%20detect%20other%2C%20less%20common%20cancers%20that%20an%20HPV%20screening%20wouldn't%20pick%20up.%20During%20a%20pelvic%20exam%2C%20a%20doctor%20may%20also%20notice%20other%20concerns%20like%20abnormal%20warts%20or%20veins%2C%20and%20can%20spot%20signs%20of%20endometriosis%2C%20fibroids%2C%20skin%20issues%2C%20abnormal%20masses%2C%20or%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20women%20avoid%20staying%20up%20to%20date%20on%20pelvic%20exams%20and%20Pap%20smears%2C%20sometimes%20because%20of%20a%20past%20sexual%20trauma.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20she%20says%20some%20of%20her%20patients%20collect%20their%20own%20HPV%20test%20samples%20in%20her%20office%20during%20their%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20somebody%20who%20can't%20or%20isn't%20comfortable%20accessing%20gynecologic%20care%2C%20a%20test%20that%20allows%20at-home%20HPV%20screening%20could%20be%20really%20impactful%2C%26quot%3B%20Flink-Bochacki%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d487cfd1-e4f8-46e4-827a-ea4db15477aa%5C%22%3EA%20deadly%20but%20preventable%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20woman%20in%20a%20hospital%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b1216fcb546d2d4d0550%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20it's%20not%20caught%20early%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20very%20tough%20to%20treat.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201940s%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20was%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20cancer%20death%20for%20women%20in%20the%20US.%20With%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20Pap%20smears%20in%20the%201940s%20and%20then%20the%20first%20HPV%20vaccine%20in%202006%2C%20cases%20and%20deaths%20have%20declined%20sharply.%20There%20are%20still%20disparities%20in%20who%20gets%20screened%20and%20treated%2C%20with%20minorities%20and%20women%20living%20in%20rural%20areas%20often%20lagging%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20seen%20those%20patients%2C%20again%2C%20although%20there%20are%20not%20many%20of%20them%2C%20each%20one%20of%20those%20is%20a%20really%20significant%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Frey%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20often%20very%20young%20women%20who%20are%20otherwise%20healthy%2C%20and%20who%20should%20have%20had%20a%20normal%20lifespan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20widespread%20HPV%20vaccination%2C%20plus%20adequate%20cancer%20screening%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20essentially%20prevent%20cervical%20cancer.%20In%20Australia%2C%20at-home%20HPV%20tests%2C%20coupled%20with%20widespread%20HPV%20vaccination%2C%20have%20the%20country%20on%20track%20to%20end%20cervical%20cancer%20as%20a%20public%20health%20issue%20by%202035%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancercouncil.com.au%2Fresearch-pt%2Feliminating-cervical-cancer-in-australia-by-2035%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECancer%20Council%20NSW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20areas%20of%20the%20world%20where%20screening%20and%20HPV%20vaccination%20are%20not%20as%20accessible%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20still%20a%20major%20concern%20and%20a%20top%20cause%20of%20cancer%20death%20for%20women.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancer.org%2Fresearch%2Facs-research-news%2Fcervical-cancer-leads-cancer-deaths-37-countries.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20American%20Cancer%20Society%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20still%20the%20deadliest%20cancer%20for%20women%20in%2037%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeal's%20at-home%20cervical%20cancer%20screening%20test%20will%20be%20available%20to%20patients%20in%20California%20starting%20in%20June.%20The%20company%20says%20it%20will%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20big%20health%20insurers%2C%20including%20Aetna%2C%20Cigna%2C%20and%20Anthem%20Blue%20Cross%20Blue%20Shield.%20There%20will%20also%20be%20a%20cash%20pay%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20you'll%20see%20us%20go%20to%20the%20other%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Egan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fat-home-pap-smear-wand-approved-fda-teal-health-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746802200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681dfcf5a466d2b74ab57dfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fat-home-pap-smear-wand-approved-fda-teal-health-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20at-home%20Pap%20smear%20is%20just%20as%20accurate%20as%20a%20doctor's%20office%20test%20for%20cervical%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fat-home-pap-smear-wand-approved-fda-teal-health-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Studio71%20Launches%20AI-Powered%20Service%20to%20Streamline%20Multiplatform%20Digital%20Publishing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746801900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp