%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistake-first-all-inclusive-resort-how-to-plan-trip-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20trip%20to%20Belize%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20go%20scuba%20diving%2C%20which%20was%20fantastic.%20After%2010%20months%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%20and%20a%20month%20later%2C%20he%20proposed%20to%20me%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20as%20we%20sat%20beside%20our%20colorful%2C%20twinkling%20tree%20and%20warm%2C%20cozy%20fireplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b04e6101-b92b-4b4c-9f11-548c6b71110f%5C%22%3EWe%20haven't%20stopped%20traveling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEleven%20months%20later%2C%20we%20got%20married%2C%20and%20the%20day%20after%2C%20we%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20beach%20and%20agreed%20that%20after%20tasting%20adventure%20together%20in%20Belize%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20much%20longer%20trip%20and%20officially%20become%20vagabonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20later%2C%20we%20quit%20our%20jobs%2C%20sold%20our%20cars%2C%20put%20everything%20else%20into%20storage%2C%20bought%20two%20backpacks%2C%20and%20flew%20to%20Bangkok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20traveled%20with%20just%20a%20Lonely%20Planet%20guidebook%20as%20we%20made%20our%20way%20through%20Thailand%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Bali.%20Four%20glorious%20months%20of%20nothing%20but%20adventures.%20We%20learned%20early%20on%20how%20to%20overcome%20difficulties%20and%20cope%20with%20constant%20change%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEighteen%20years%20after%20our%20first%20big%20adventure%20trip%2C%20we%20lost%20our%20jobs%20due%20to%20an%20economic%20downturn%2C%20so%20we%20took%20off%20again%20for%20a%20six-month%20trip%20to%20Bali%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20and%20India.%20Then%2C%20after%20a%20year%20back%20home%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20house%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20seven-month%20trip%20that%20included%20the%20Greek%20Islands%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Laos%2C%20and%20back%20to%20Thailand%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3