y%20shouldn't%20be%20lonely%20and%20sad%20and%20anxiety-inducing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaurov%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20money%20is%20behind%20every%20decision%20that%20you%20make%20in%20life%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20scary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20Kaurov%20thinks%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20making%2C%20and%20what%20they%20can%20do%20to%20fix%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ee0d433-aed6-463d-ab46-1b00ac2dd670%5C%22%3E1.%20Believing%20everything%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%2C%20especially%20TikTok%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-finance-tiktok-gets-wrong-about-saving-money-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull%20of%20financial%20advice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Not%20all%20of%20it%20is%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaurov%20said%20that%20while%20TikToks%20and%20Instagram%20Reels%20are%20great%20for%20opening%20up%20the%20conversation%20about%20money%2C%20much%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20really%20verified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20a%2017-year-old%20TikTok%20who%20is%20like%2C%20this%20is%20how%20I%20built%20a%20seven-figure%20business%20overnight%2C%20I'm%2017%20and%20I'm%20already%20retired.%20I%20think%20it%20creates%20very%20unrealistic%20portrayals%20of%20how%20people%20are%20managing%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20creates%20an%20idea%20that%20Gen%20Z%20has%20it%20together%20with%20money%2C%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20most%20people%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20people%20shouldn't%20compare%20themselves%20to%20these%20posts%2C%20Kaurov%20said%2C%20and%20instead%20think%20about%20their%20own%20goals%20and%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e20ba2b-33bd-4c8a-8b8f-e583413f49f6%5C%22%3E2.%20Not%20getting%20real%20about%20credit%20card%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Zers%20are%20racking%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerati