%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rescript%20team%20comprises%20nine%20people%20who%20look%20after%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20stationery%20items%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Rescript%20team%20comprises%20nine%20people%20who%20look%20after%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20stationery%20items%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratik%20Dawda%2C%20who%20has%20been%20with%20Rescript%20for%20over%203.5%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20lead%20all%20our%20digital%20marketing%20efforts%2C%20including%20paid%20ads%2C%20content%2C%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20WhatsApp%20communications%2C%20and%20performance%20strategy.%20I%20also%20support%20B2B%20lead%20generation%20and%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20our%20web%2C%20product%2C%20and%20design%20teams%20to%20grow%20our%20online%20presence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Rescript%2C%20we%20are%20hands-on%2C%20intentional%2C%20and%20honest.%20We%20do%20not%20chase%20trends%2C%20instead%2C%20we%20f