0products%2C%20clients%20receive%20a%20detailed%20summary%20showing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255790%2Fslug-ladakh-save-crores-village-dah-hanu-valley-apricots-trees-yellow-tail-moth-pest-tsering-stobdan-pest-eradication-organic-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20trees%20saved%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20water%20conserved%2C%20and%20carbon%20emissions%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20one%20thing%20to%20say%20a%20product%20is%20sustainable.%20It%20is%20another%20way%20to%20show%20clients%20the%20actual%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20say%20the%20co-founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescript%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20still%20unfolding.%20But%20every%20page%20turned%20and%20every%20sheet%20printed%20is%20a%20small%20yet%20moving%20act%20of%20environmental%20responsibility.%20In%20a%20time%20when%20we%20are%20figuring%20out%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341870%2Fhygenco-first-green-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20climate%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Naren%20and%20Ashutosh%20believe%20meaningful%20change%20can%20begin%20with%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20the%20paper%20on%20your%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Rescript%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746718190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D426169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Childhood%20friends%20Naren%20Raj%20and%20Ashutosh%20Ananth%20are%20the%20co-founders%20of%20Rescript%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20sustainable%20stationery%20brand%20that%20is%20reshaping%20how%20India%20thinks%20about%20paper.%20By%20turning%20waste%20pa