%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20harvest%20barley%2C%20we%20grind%20it%20into%20a%20flour%20using%20the%20water%20mill%2C%20which%20does%20not%20use%20any%20electricity.%20Its%20principle%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20a%20hydroelectric%20plant.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20two-storey%20structure%20where%20the%20turbine%20powers%20the%20flow%20of%20water%2C%20which%20turns%20the%20stone%2C%20which%20grinds%20the%20barley%20into%20a%20powder%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tsetan%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiachen%20Naturals%E2%80%99%20offerings%20include%20barley%20soup%20with%20added%20dried%20tomato%20and%20mushroom%2C%20nettle%20soup%2C%20and%20barley%20porridge%3B%20the%20plans%20of%20expanding%20the%20menu%20are%20in%20the%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20equitable%20business%20model%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20nervous%20to%20let%20her%20kids%20venture%20into%20farming%20territory%2C%20Tsering%20now%20encourages%20them%20towards%20it.%20After%20revelling%20in%20success%20through%20the%20model%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F249068%2Fladakh-farmer-earns-lakhs-organic-farming-self-sustaining-farm-gya-village-urgain-phuntsog-income-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers%20in%20Siachen%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20changing%20their%20stance%20towards%20agriculture%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20viable%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20his%20own%20experiences%20in%202019%2C%20when%20he%20returned%20home%20and%20told%20his%20parents%20his%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20a%20farmer%2C%20Tsetan%20says%20they%20discouraged%20him%20from%20it.%20After%20coaxing%20them%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20the%20easiest%20part%20of%20the%20battle.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20got%20into%20farming%2C%20I%20noticed%20how%2C%20despite%20people%20working%20so%20hard%2C%20they%20hardly%20earned%20enough.%20It%20was%20the%20same