tural%20Movement%20of%20Ladakh)%2C%20which%20he%20joined%20after%20Class%2011.%20The%20year%20he%20spent%20at%20SECMOL%20was%20transformational%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F409442%2Fvolunteer-organisations-travel-purpose-wildlife-farming-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20programmes%20%3C%2Fa%3Egave%20him%20some%20measure%20of%20an%20informed%20opinion%20on%20the%20problems%20his%20land%20was%20facing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20understood%20about%20the%20environmental%20problems%2C%20about%20how%20migrations%20and%20modernisation%20are%20affecting%20the%20community.%20The%20learning%20was%20hands-on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tsetan%20notes.%20He%20began%20to%20understand%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20pain%20points.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20quit%20farming%20because%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20getting%20a%20significant%20income%20from%20it.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20families%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20had%20joined%20the%20BRO%20(Border%20Roads%20Organisation)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tsetan%20discovered.%20Farmers%20had%20traded%20their%20agency%20for%20a%20steady%20source%20of%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-13-1746610149.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Siachen%20Naturals%20range%20of%20products%20include%20various%20kinds%20of%20soups%20that%20feature%20dried%20herbs%2C%20cheese%20and%20fruits%20in%20them%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-13-1746610149.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-13-1746610149-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe