ugh%20to%20ask%20me%20for%20collaborations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Companies%20pay%20her%20to%20display%20their%20logos%20on%20her%20Thar%2C%20leveraging%20its%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaaji%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20have%20a%20sufficient%20bank%20balance%20before%20starting%20a%20trip.%20%E2%80%9CI%20look%20at%20my%20expenses%20daily.%20If%20I%20have%20enough%20for%20fuel%2C%20food%20and%20other%20expenses%2C%20I%20am%20good%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20adds%20Naaji%2C%20who%20hopes%20that%20tomorrow%20will%20be%20a%20better%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98If%20you%20can%20travel%20in%20India%2C%20you%20can%20travel%20anywhere%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaaji%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20safety%20is%20rooted%20in%20her%20extensive%20travels%20across%20India%2C%20which%20she%20considers%20the%20ultimate%20training%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20travelled%20the%20whole%20of%20India%20five%20times.%20This%20is%20a%20bigger%20experience%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20to%20other%20countries%20with%20ease.%20If%20you%20can%20travel%20in%20India%2C%20you%20can%20travel%20anywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20acknowledging%20that%20%E2%80%98a%20lot%20of%20people%20assume%20that%20India%20is%20not%20safe%20for%20women%20travellers%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20%E2%80%98in%20certain%20places%2C%20things%20become%20a%20little%20tricky%2C%E2%80%99%20she%20emphasises%20the%20inherent%20goodness%20of%20people%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-06T193213.064-1746540280.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naaji%20sitting%20on%20her%20car%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co